# SUBMISSION PROJECT

    Sebuah aplikasi golang sederhana yang terhubung ke database PostgreSQL.

## DESKRIPSI

    Submission Project dari Enigma Camp materi Golang Database dengan nama challenge-godb.

## FITUR

    1. MENU UTAMA:
        - CUSTOMER
        - SERVICE
        - ORDER
        - EXIT

    2. MENU CUSTOMER:
        - Create Customer
        - View of List Customer
        - View Details Customer by ID
        - Update Customer
        - Delete Customer

    3. MENU SERVICE:
        - Create Service
        - VIew of List Service
        - View Details Service by ID
        - Update Service
        - Delete Service

    4. MENU ORDER:
        - Create Order
        - Complete Order
        - View of List Order
        - View Order Details by ID

## REQUIRMENTS

    1. Golang: Versi minimal Go 1.18
    2. PostgreSQL
    3. Clone Repo (Optional)

## INSTALASI

    1. Clone Repo Project ini:
        - git clone https://github.com/Darari17/challenge-godb.git
        - cd challenge-godb

    2. Install Dependencies:
        - go mod tidy

    3. Setup database:
        - Buat database baru di PostgreSQL:
            CREATE DATABASE enigma_laundry;

        - Sesuaikan informasi koneksi di file main.go:
            const (
                host     = "localhost"
                port     = 5432
                user     = "postgres"
                password = "12345"
                dbname   = "enigma_laundry"
            )

    4. Jalankan Aplikasi:
        - go run main.go

